1
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:10,400
Simón Pedro iuan okse nomachtijketl kikuitlapanuiyayaj Jesús.

2
00:00:10,400 --> 00:00:16,280
On okse nomachtijketl kixmatiya on más ueyi intlayekankau on tiopixkej.

3
00:00:16,280 --> 00:00:16,960
Yejua ika,

4
00:00:16,960 --> 00:00:20,840
no okalak iuan Jesús ipan ikiauak on tlayekanki.

5
00:00:20,840 --> 00:00:24,280
Pero Pedro onokau kiauatenko.

6
00:00:24,280 --> 00:00:25,000
Yejua ika,

7
00:00:25,000 --> 00:00:35,080
on nomachtijketl yejuan kixmatiya inmasueyitlayekankau on tiopixkej okisako niman otlajtlajtoj iuan on siuatl yejuan tlapiya ne kiauatenko,

8
00:00:35,080 --> 00:00:36,880
niman okalaktij Pedro.

9
00:00:36,880 --> 00:00:41,160
Kemaj on siuatl yejuan tlapixki ipan on kiauatempan,

10
00:00:41,160 --> 00:00:43,280
ijkin okitlajtoltij Pedro:

11
00:00:43,280 --> 00:00:48,000
—¿Tlen tejua xno tiitemachtijkau on tlakatl?

12
00:00:48,000 --> 00:00:49,520
Pedro okijtoj:

13
00:00:49,520 --> 00:00:50,200
—Ka,

14
00:00:50,200 --> 00:00:51,680
nejua ka.

15
00:00:51,680 --> 00:01:00,520
On tekitkej niman on policías okitlalijkaj tlitl de tekojli niman majmaniyaj nototonijtikatkaj pampa seuaya.

16
00:01:00,520 --> 00:01:05,760
Pedro no ompa inuan nemiya nototonijtikatka itech on tlitl.

17
00:01:05,760 --> 00:01:13,080
On tlayekanketl intech on tiopixkej okitlajtoltij Jesús de on inomachtijkauan*,

18
00:01:13,080 --> 00:01:15,360
niman de on tlen kitemachtiaya.

19
00:01:15,360 --> 00:01:17,680
Jesús okinmijlij:

20
00:01:17,680 --> 00:01:20,400
—Nejua onitlajtlajtoj ixpan nochi tlakatl.

21
00:01:20,400 --> 00:01:28,800
Nochipa nitemachtiaya ipan on sinagogas* niman ipan on ueyitiopan kampa nosentlaliaj nochimej on hebreos*.

22
00:01:28,800 --> 00:01:29,680
Ijkon tej,

23
00:01:29,680 --> 00:01:31,400
xitlaj* san onikichtakaijtoj.

24
00:01:31,400 --> 00:01:33,680
¿Tline* nejua tinechtlajtoltia?

25
00:01:33,680 --> 00:01:36,520
Xkintlajtolti on yejuan nechkakiyaj.

26
00:01:36,520 --> 00:01:39,640
Yejuamej ma kijtokan tlinon nikimijliaya.

27
00:01:39,640 --> 00:01:42,800
Yejuamej kimatstokej tlinon nikinmachtiaya.

28
00:01:42,800 --> 00:01:45,000
Ijkuak Jesús ijkon okijtoj,

29
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:50,700
sen ipolicía on ueyitiopan yejuan ompa nemiya okixayakauitektiaj,

30
00:01:50,700 --> 00:01:52,760
niman okijlij:

31
00:01:52,760 --> 00:01:56,880
—¿Ijkon tiknankilia on más ueyi intlayekankau on tiopixkej?

32
00:01:56,880 --> 00:01:58,160
Jesús okijlij:

33
00:01:58,160 --> 00:02:00,720
—Tla itlaj xkuajli onikijtoj,

34
00:02:00,720 --> 00:02:02,440
xkijto tline xkuajli.

35
00:02:02,440 --> 00:02:04,760
Pero tla kuajli on tlen onikijto,

36
00:02:04,760 --> 00:02:06,640
¿tline tinechmailia?

37
00:02:06,640 --> 00:02:13,300
Kemaj Anás okititlan itech Caifás on yejuan inmasueyitlayekankau on tiopixkej.

38
00:02:13,300 --> 00:02:16,580
Jesús sanken*  salijtiaya.

39
00:02:16,580 --> 00:02:21,160
Chika Pedro sanken* nototonijtikatka itech on tlitl,

40
00:02:21,160 --> 00:02:22,560
okijlijkej:

41
00:02:22,560 --> 00:02:26,360
—¿Tejua xno tiitemachtijkau on tlakatl?

42
00:02:26,360 --> 00:02:27,680
Niman Pedro*,

43
00:02:27,680 --> 00:02:28,540
okijtoj:

44
00:02:28,540 --> 00:02:29,200
—Ka,

45
00:02:29,200 --> 00:02:29,960
nejua ka.

46
00:02:29,960 --> 00:02:35,540
Kemaj se itekichiuilijkau on tlayekanketl itech on tiopixkej,

47
00:02:35,540 --> 00:02:39,840
yejuan ken kitaya on tlakatl yejuan Pedro okinakastsonteka,

48
00:02:39,840 --> 00:02:41,920
ijkin okitlajtoltij:

49
00:02:41,920 --> 00:02:45,720
—¿Xiuan onimitsitak ne ipan kojtlakijloj?

50
00:02:45,720 --> 00:02:48,080
Pedro oksejpa okinenek*,

51
00:02:48,080 --> 00:02:53,520
niman kemaj nimantsin otsajtsik sen kaxtil*.

